{"tid":1439313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【出路討論】要有方法比和理非參與運動","createTime":"2019-08-10T05:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T13:02:50.000Z","uid":39021,"like":76,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"4cdc22fb90c7e7bb426d1e183f3b5f6768f9bba2","tid":1439313,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:19:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">－－－前言－－－</span></strong><br />\n政府主動出擊，將會以安全為由禁止一切大型遊行<br />\n此舉令和理非無法參與活動，政府就可以慢慢瓦解民氣<br />\n所以我地要做既野係：<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>確保和理非可以繼續參與運動！！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">－－－對策一：大量小型遊行－－－</span></strong><br />\n今日星期六朝上分別有兩場遊行：親子遊行及銀髮遊行<br />\n代表乜野？就係警方無法拒絕非常指定性既遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n接下來可以遍地開花，<strong>用不同名目於多區組織遊行</strong><br />\n例子：天文界激光遊行、女權反黑警性暴力遊行、勞工拒中資遊行、醫學界人道危機遊行、城大畢業生反送中遊行<br />\n<strong>呢個方法更可以令到遊離派睇到香港各界都有人反政府！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">－－－對策二：商場行街－－－</span></strong><br />\n而家和理非最驚就係無緣無故被拒捕，所以部份人士不敢參與未得到「不反對通知書」既遊行<br />\n既然機場運動咁安全，點解唔方便大家，將類似行動都放喺唔同商場上？<br />\n每星期集中人群光顧三四個商場，沿途向街坊遊客做文宣<br />\n<strong>嘆冷氣！低風險！聚民氣！阻消費！門檻極極極極低！</strong><br />\n如果商場唔比人坐，我地可以係咁行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果商場趕人走，我地可以突擊其他商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f1e9f459c0ae1bf7a468b722a57286b4e87f0732","tid":1439313,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf09c9df72ab5ab1417e43958781e44729ff4db","tid":1439313,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:20:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">推行動post呀<br />\n<br />\n 【置頂+廣傳】８.１０ 大 埔 逃 生 路 線 圖 （附 廣 場 名）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438647</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span>"},{"pid":"68eb735fbd098045dcf2964ffb61dfa2dc3a3560","tid":1439313,"uid":82194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:20:41.000Z","msg":"[民間記者會]要贏民意，除咗做到政府做唔到嘅野，仲要做到大眾覺得我地做唔到嘅野。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439252\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439252</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c4f078ef94576b78a44e3be3efa4ec72cefc937f","tid":1439313,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80a2c1fab927d37444a295f21de6457ba6f8160","tid":1439313,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:23:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02403eb3176241657b31feb650b3218e8f39bbf","tid":1439313,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c2a4ffd4873645b119891acfe35109fef298ec","tid":1439313,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c